In her New York Times best-seller, The Truths We Hold: An American Journey, Kamala Harris, one of America’s most inspiring political leaders, wants the future generation to hear, learn and be encouraged by action that she and many others are taking. “I don’t want us to just tell them how we felt,” she writes. “I want us to tell them what we did.”



